cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about applying neural networks to natural language processing tasks with structured output, and enforcing deterministic constraints on the output values. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories related to natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). Among these, cs.CL is the most likely category as the paper specifically focuses on natural language processing tasks.
